{"tid":518528,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)環太平洋 超級戰艦 人造天劫 黑魔塔","createTime":"2018-01-03T12:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T19:46:26.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9654884f0a28481174238e4df102417f54ad9072","tid":518528,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=e4b537b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=728a7a2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://screenwriterleo.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/%E7%92%B0%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%93%E5%A4%A2%E6%99%82%E5%88%BB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscreenwriterleo.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F07%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%259C%2593%25E5%25A4%25A2%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2588%25BB.jpg&h=e5eaf5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6e/Battleship_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6e%2FBattleship_Poster.jpg&h=6e951f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f5/Geostorm_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff5%2FGeostorm_Poster.jpg&h=f79748bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9a/The_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg&h=d22264de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.2013年，環太平洋地區海底深處出現了一個平行宇宙「突破點」，隨後，一個巨大無比的巨獸生物從「海洋」中崛起，第一隻巨獸首先摧毀了舊金山以及周圍所有的海岸城市，而人類大部分企圖阻止巨獸的軍事行動全部以失敗告終，但巨獸也最終在人類的殊死抵抗下死於核彈中，但舊金山方圓百里變成了荒蕪之地。事件結束後，人類爲巨獸起了「怪獸」（Kaiju）的名字，但原本認為結束的怪獸襲擊卻接二連三而出現在各個環太平洋城市。人類在無計可施之下發明了他們自己創造的「怪獸」：「機甲獵人」（Jaeger），利用巨大機械士兵來對抗怪獸大軍，由兩名腦部神經網路互相串連（浮動神經元連結）的操縱者同步操作戰鬥機械士兵，利用儀器來檢測怪獸的級別與代號。自從有了機甲獵人，人類開始獲得勝利，甚至將怪獸襲擊變成宣傳活動與儀式，但人類卻並不知道更加恐怖的威脅即將來臨，而「怪獸戰役」也就此打響.......<br />\n<br />\n2.公元2005年，美國國家航空暨太空總署（NASA）發現了一個太陽系外的類地行星。由於研判該行星可能存在智慧生命，NASA自夏威夷通信陣列基地透過天上的人造衛星發射高功率信號，加以試探。<br />\n外星人5艘星艦不久遠道而來，卻因為當中的通訊艦誤撞人造衛星而墜毀，碎片墜落於香港，造成約略兩萬多人傷亡。而其他4艘艦艇則降落於夏威夷附近。恰巧夏威夷附近正在舉行環太平洋演習（RIMPAC），包括美國海軍與日本海上自衛隊的軍艦皆參與了該活動，聯合艦隊指揮官夏恩上將（Admiral Terrance Shane）命令美國海軍神盾驅逐艦桑普森號（USS Sampson DDG-102）帶領僚艦約翰‧保羅‧瓊斯號（USS John Paul Jones DDG-53）與前來參與演習的日本海上自衛隊神盾飛彈護衛艦妙高號<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述當地球上的天候已呈現失控狀態時，人類能依靠天候控制衛星來控制天候。但某日，該衛星竟因未知原因而發生故障，使得地球上的天候發生暴走，各種毀滅性的天災降臨城市、造成嚴重災害<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述在文明崩壞世界中，羅蘭&middot;德斯欽是名主要以雙左輪手槍為武器的僅存槍客，他希望能在宇宙的中樞「黑塔」找到阻止自己世界滅亡的方法<br />\n<br />\n8 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=01647abb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=b75d0006\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10623866c8afb97c8c7c39ba2f93dca870dd428f","tid":518528,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac5e67c537d5d674956ddba52446f4da4cc4063","tid":518528,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f397495a9d1e020c72147bfd4b4f56ab2617893","tid":518528,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e202c5fc22166696d0a862061d1b9c6c4bc0b583","tid":518528,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc2b7f6e8bdefbffaac888eb4cb3bf834e2a2ba","tid":518528,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"黑魔塔好似係垃圾片"},{"pid":"63c7239e75478fcbd5bbff637c36e466a7e1ab4d","tid":518528,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb92fe6693e595daaded68ba93567a5eb86ed8df","tid":518528,"uid":29160,